   Release Notes:
   ____________________________________________________________________

	2008 release, the first official live album from Whitney 
	featuring the fabulous R&B/Soul diva captured in concert 
	in Norfolk, VA on March 31, 1991. Whitney is in great form 
	as she belts her way through some of her biggest hits 
	including &#039;How Will I Know&#039;, &#039;The Greatest Love Of All&#039; 
	and &#039;I Wanna Dance With Somebody (Who Loves Me)&#039;. Also 
	contains Houston performing a stunning medley that 
	features &#039;Didn&#039;t We Almost Have It All&#039;, &#039;A House Is Not 
	A Home&#039; and &#039;Where Do Broken Hearts Go&#039;. A great release 
	for any Whitney and Pop/R&B fan.
